WEBVTT

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:34.376
If you can, you're beginning
to see the face

00:01:34.400 --> 00:01:36.816
of the invisible wounds of war,

00:01:36.840 --> 00:01:39.696
commonly known
as post-traumatic stress disorder

00:01:39.720 --> 00:01:41.160
and traumatic brain injury.

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:45.016
While I can't say I have
post-traumatic stress disorder,

00:01:45.040 --> 00:01:46.960
I've never been a stranger to it.

00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:51.800
When I was a little girl, I would visit
my grandparents every summer.

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:53.976
It was my grandfather

00:01:54.000 --> 00:01:57.400
who introduced me to the effects
of combat on the psyche.

